  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072190/extras/d8c74d9a5b6d583c455be285faa6caaa.avif?t=1688448824\" width=400 height=200 /></span><br>Cursed Colors is a roguelite game, where the key to success lies on destroying enemies by matching different colors while you attack.<br>Every enemy has it weakness, exploit it to get an advantage and progress through the world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072190/extras/62d6575ee043b62883588cf796b326de.avif?t=1688448824\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>If you fail, you start over.<br>But each time you fail you can get upgrades at the shop with loot dropped from your enemies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072190/extras/5ff9f2708931736a8c1bb7c6d486519b.avif?t=1688448824\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>Try out different combinations of upgrades and characters in order to optimize your favorite playstyle.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Content</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Thematic stages with different enemies and backgrounds.<br></li><li>5 unlockable characters with different skills.<br></li><li>Original Soundtracks for each stage.<br></li><li>Challenging boss fights.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072190/extras/d8c74d9a5b6d583c455be285faa6caaa.avif?t=1688448824\" width=400 height=200 /></span><br>Cursed Colors is a roguelite game, where the key to success lies on destroying enemies by matching different colors while you attack.<br>Every enemy has it weakness, exploit it to get an advantage and progress through the world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072190/extras/62d6575ee043b62883588cf796b326de.avif?t=1688448824\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>If you fail, you start over.<br>But each time you fail you can get upgrades at the shop with loot dropped from your enemies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072190/extras/5ff9f2708931736a8c1bb7c6d486519b.avif?t=1688448824\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>Try out different combinations of upgrades and characters in order to optimize your favorite playstyle.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Content</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Thematic stages with different enemies and backgrounds.<br></li><li>5 unlockable characters with different skills.<br></li><li>Original Soundtracks for each stage.<br></li><li>Challenging boss fights.</li></ul>",
